name: Simulator
body: ### Welcome This is page for the code maintained on github. This contains limited source that can be used to run the go based simulator on local linux PC. ``` $ mkdir project $ cd project $ git clone git@github.com:wiless/simulator.git ``` ### Release Notes ### Feature Requests ### Authors and Contributors Some modules are suported by @oldmonk. ### Support or Contact Interact with us on Google+
